Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,牠跟得上我的動作!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,和今天遇到的怪物完全不能比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是 強化種!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,別貿然追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不、不行 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,攻擊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快閃開!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,千草大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,逃走了? 怪物竟然會逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,千草!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,振作點 千草
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,綠色的苔蘚 將吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.38,0:02:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 放過我們...
